---
title: Creamy Rosé Tortellini with Roasted Red Peppers
description: This one is just like your favourite restaurant's cheesy tortellini! The creamy rosé sauce coats every piece of pasta and the gooey mozzarella cheese makes for an unforgettable takeout fake-out.
